		SwiftSmallText1: "Rapid Development: Swift is a modern programming language specifically designed for developing iOS, macOS, watchOS, and tvOS applications. It was built with the goal of making development more efficient and productive. Swift code is clean and well-structured, leading to faster development and fewer errors.",
